## SWOT

#Strength
* It will give an account holder all the information he wants
* User do not have to worry about managing their hard copy as all the details will be here
* User can see all previous details in this 
* It gives user an interface that makes it interesting

#Weakness
* It does not provide high level of security as anyone with information can view the details
* It do not have the apply for loan or see if you are eligible for loan

#Opportunity
* We are going to learn many new concepts like Inheritance, Polymorphism, Encapsulation and Abstraction
* We can store our data using database from that we are going to learn some concept of database also

#Threat
* There is slight chance that our information can be missused
